('prt_f563cb70d001ndmDCTFxqiknNX', 'msg_f563cae14001Wp27GNilMkKg5l', 'ses_0a9ca56e7ffemkhtFjqbhgDpj8', 1783858247437, 1783858250659, '{"type":"reasoning","text":"Done! The migration was successful. Let me summarize what was done:\n1. Created a new project record for `D:/BaiduSyncdisk/all_code/candywall-skills`\n2. Updated 3 sessions from `global` project to the new parent directory project\n3. Updated the directory field of those sessions to point to the parent directory\n\nNow the user should be able to run the backup script successfully.","time":{"start":1783858247437,"end":1783858250658}}'),
